    <command xml:space="preserve">go e</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Ravine&#x000A;A deep natural ravine carved into warm, mineral-rich rock.&#x000A;&#x000A;You can see Xilar here.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
